{"type":"question","id":24317,"title":"如何评价Ruw批评某日本网友在一张科普东方Project图中提到zun认可二创（多图警告）？","uid":19778,"topics":[81,32,7081,88,4004],"contents":"发布者：THBWiki官方账户<br>\n日本热心网友制作了一个科普东方Project构成的图片，却因图中提到zun认可二次创作，而遭到负责管理整个东方版权的上海爱丽丝幻乐团要员Ruw的批评。 <br>\n以下是Ruw的话： <br>\n———————— <br>\n这种会引发误解的插画传播开来的话就难办了 ・东方Project本身不包含二次创作 ・ZUN先生本人并没有以官方进行认可的个人二次创作 ・二次创作的范畴不包含剧场版&nbsp; 无论哪一幅插画都有会招致误解的地方，是不适当的，而且这种对比也会导致东方的印象变差，是坏棋一步 <br>\n————————<br>\n注：日语【公认】指 官方形式进行认可&nbsp; Ruw话语里似乎认为东方Project一词不包含二次创作，且表达了一种zun不认可二次创作的意味（日语里公认一词十分不正式），在日本引发了诸多讨论。&nbsp;&nbsp; <br>\n原链接：https://twitter.com/Ruw/status/1253973083834077184&nbsp; <br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/s09xhCZ.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/s09xhCZ.png\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/s09xhCZ.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/ncFmgzY.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/ncFmgzY.png\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/ncFmgzY.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/ab79WR9.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/ab79WR9.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/ab79WR9.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/A0upsIy_d.webp?maxwidth=640&amp;shape=thumb&amp;fidelity=medium\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/A0upsIy_d.webp?maxwidth=640&amp;shape=thumb&amp;fidelity=medium\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/A0upsIy_d.webp?maxwidth=640&amp;shape=thumb&amp;fidelity=medium\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n附当天幻奏群发言：<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/3iTXGQW.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/3iTXGQW.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/3iTXGQW.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/Tb0HQ40.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Tb0HQ40.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/Tb0HQ40.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n（维 新 修 约）<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/2VXWkYm.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/2VXWkYm.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/2VXWkYm.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n（你们是说你们怀疑Ruw要搞令和政变，架空zun，自己当日本车万圈天皇，实行独裁统治，然后对日本东方圈搞大清洗，再搞个（天）津（江）户合流，和赵旭升做最好的独裁者兄弟？）<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/QtiZt2c.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/QtiZt2c.png\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/QtiZt2c.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/slsbNYd.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/slsbNYd.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/slsbNYd.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n（哇浪，这么厉害？！赶紧的，出征zunteam）<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/1T6JDf6.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/1T6JDf6.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/1T6JDf6.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/TddeMZ5.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/TddeMZ5.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/TddeMZ5.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/1CB5uYe.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/1CB5uYe.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/1CB5uYe.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n（当然啦，因为幻奏群人均战狼，在他们看来：“这小日本鬼儿算什么东西？！”）<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/x18mAD2.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/x18mAD2.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/x18mAD2.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n（要出征力，要出征力）<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/9Tq1IKA.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/9Tq1IKA.jpg\" alt=\"https://